high_descs: Go to the stove that is directly behind you.
Pick up the teakettle from the stove.
Turn right and go clockwise along the counter on your left, until you come to the sink, then face the sink.
Fill the teakettle with water at the sink.
Return to the stove, carrying the filled kettle.
Put the kettle on the right front stove burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a filled teakettle onto the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and face the stove
Pick up a kettle off of the stove
Make your way left and then right until you are facing the sink
Put the kettle in to the sink and run the faucet for a few seconds, then pick the kettle back up
Return to your position facing the stove
Put the kettle back down on the stove
Turn around to your left then face the stove
Pick up the kettle on the stove
Turn to your right walk straight then head to the sink
Put the kettle in the sink then rinse it
Turn left then left again head to the stove
Put the clean kettle on the right side of the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the clean kettle on the stove
